About Me
I’m Aneequa, a proactive intern passionate about UI/UX design,
branding, and web development. Through hands-on internships at
Oasis Infobyte and FutureIntern, I’m gaining practical experience in
building responsive interfaces and creating professional graphics
using tools like GitHub, Replit, Canva, and Coolab.ai.. I thrive on
blending creativity with precision, and I’m committed to growing
my skills through real-world projects and structured learning.
